Package mil.nga.geopackage.extension.nga.contents

Class ContentsIdExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.geopackage.extension.BaseExtension
      • mil.nga.geopackage.extension.nga.contents.ContentsIdExtension
  • public class ContentsIdExtension
extends BaseExtension
    This extension assigns a unique integer identifier to tables defined in the contents. Allows foreign key referencing to a contents (text based primary key) by an integer identifier.

    http://ngageoint.github.io/GeoPackage/docs/extensions/contents-id.html

    Since:
    3.2.0
    Author:
    osbornb
